originalText.text: This is probably the latest place opening wise you could go to get your mail done. The place is tightly packed they don't speak English or they didn't when I went there and there's barely room for anyone much less accessibility. The only thing that gives this place any Merit at all is that they have a 30 inch screen with the news on while you wait and you will wait.

originalText.text: UPS website and customer service says Bella Vista is open on Sunday at 10am. I went there and they are closed. UPS should have accurate information when designating pickup locations for its packages. I will do my best to not use them again.

originalText.text:
Just amazing..

If you want a taste of why New Yorker are considered rude and unprofessional just visit this location.  Do not go if you are looking for any type of service professional or not.  Apparently this location is open just for looks and although they offer many services such as Fedex Pick up they have not intention of actually doing their job.  They actually don’t even have the equipment needed for this job.  If you are ok with your package maybe being pickup, maybe not, maybe being delivered, maybe being lost then this is your location.  If you don’t mind being spoken to like you are bothering them this is the location.  Otherwise please don’t bother using this location as it is a waste of time and money.
